	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rogo te, <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingere</persName>, hunc virum patricii ordinis, eruditum, pium et iam consulem reipublicę <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustanae</placeName><note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName ref="p6186" cert="high">Wolfgang Rehlinger</persName>.</note>, una cum suo collega<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Syndikus Dr. <persName ref="p5170" cert="high">Konrad Heel</persName>. - Die beiden <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augsburger</placeName> suchten das Gespräch über einen eventuellen Beitritt von <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basel</placeName> und <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zürich</placeName> zum Schmalkaldischen Bund; s. Fabian, Quellen 175. Vgl. auch das Empfehlungsschreiben <persName ref="p8129" cert="high">Jakob Meyers</persName> vom 24. Mai (unten <ref target="file11042">Nr. 1000</ref>).</note> tibi commendatum habeas propter communem religionem Christi atque studium pietatis, imo periculorum affinitatem, quia nondum tam deploratę sunt res pontificiorum, quam incuriosis interim videntur.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p1974" cert="high">Lutherus</persName> instaurat pugnam contra eos.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vos vigilate, nihil contemnite, quo minus securos et oscitantes opprimant.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Concilium suum pontifex <placeName ref="l425" cert="high">Romanus</placeName><note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="p19981" cert="high">Paul III.</persName></note> in alterum annum distulit<note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4">Am 20. April war in <placeName ref="l425" cert="high">Rom</placeName> die Verschiebung des Konzils auf den 1. November desselben Jahres bekanntgegeben worden; s. Hubert <hi>Jedin,</hi> Geschichte des Konzils von Trient, Bd. I, Freiburg 1951, S. 264.</note>, quod hoc tempus ad res pro arbitrio conficiendas parum sit idoneum, et tamen indictum esse nobis detrimento est, quos illo telo confodere, quoties facultas arriserit, non dubie studebit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Professores et symmistas salvere iubeo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucerus</persName> <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augustam</placeName> abiit his diebus<note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5">Zum Aufenthalt <persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucers</persName> in <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augsburg</placeName> vom 18. Mai bis 9. Juli 1537 s. <hi>Pollet,</hi> <persName ref="p467" cert="high">Bucer</persName> II 236-238.</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">13. kalendas iunii anno 1537.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p5565" cert="high">V. Capito</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Consuli <persName ref="p2816" type="auto_name">Resthio</persName><note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="p2816" cert="high">Diethelm Röist</persName>.</note> et vestro magistratui hos, oro te, viros commenda; nam digni sunt, in quos officia nostra collocemus<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7">Die Bewirtung des <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augsburger</placeName> Bürgermeisters und seiner Begleiter ist in der Seckelamtsrechnung zwischen 24. Mai und 6. Juni vermerkt <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">(Zürich</placeName> StA, F III 32, 1536[-1537], S. 47).</note>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, viro eruditissimo atque integerrimo, ecclesię <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinę</placeName> pastori, sibi in domino suspiciendo.</s>
				</p>
